Text: Ay yo! It was getting late and I'd been messing with files for hours when I inadvertently named Milk & Cheese 05, 06 instead. The file named 06 is actually 05. The file named 06 (aka 666) IS, in fact, 06. I'm sure you, whoever you are, have it within your mental prowess to change Milk & Cheese 06 to Milk & Cheese 05. Thank you, and good night.
You're welcome two tons. Glad there's still some interest in stuff like this.
